title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“The city streets are being decimated,' by illegal dumpers, DiClaudio told the judge.” [From The Philadelphia Daily News, page 10, n.d. Submitted by Steve LaCheen, Philadelphia.]
